  <h2>How It Works: Your Selfie, Supercharged</h2>
  
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Upload your photo or fetch your profile pic from Twitter, GitHub, Mastodon, and more.</li>
    <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Choose a style for the selfie from a list of presets or modify the prompt yourself.</li>
    <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Pay with a promo code, Stripe, or even Bitcoin Lightning.</li>
    <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Get a one-of-a-kind AI-generated selfie—featuring you and your chosen star!</li>
  </ol>
  
  <p>It's fast, fun, and totally unique. No Photoshop skills required—just a little imagination.</p>

  <h2>For Influencers: Your Brand, Your Way</h2>
  
  <p>GenSelfie isn't just for fans. Influencers get a powerful admin panel to:</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li>Set up custom branding and pricing</li>
    <li>Upload reference images and create multiple selfie "presets"</li>
    <li>Manage promo codes and payments</li>
    <li>Track engagement and delight your community</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>It's a new way to connect, reward superfans, and grow your brand—powered by the latest in AI image generation.</p>

  <h2>Tech Behind the Magic: AI, Payments, and Privacy</h2>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>AI-Powered Images:</strong> GenSelfie uses a <a href="https://github.com/ValyrianTech/ComfyUI_with_Flux">ComfyUI</a> backend (with the latest FLUX2 models) to create stunning, realistic selfies.</li>
    <li><strong>Flexible Payments:</strong> Fans can pay however they like—credit card, promo code, or Bitcoin Lightning.</li>
    <li><strong>Social Media Integration:</strong> Fetch your best profile pic from all the major platforms, or upload your own.</li>
    <li><strong>Privacy First:</strong> No data is shared without your consent, and everything is open source.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why GenSelfie?</h2>
  
  <p>
    Because everyone deserves a little star power! Whether you're a fan looking for a fun keepsake, or a creator wanting to offer something special, GenSelfie makes it easy, safe, and a little bit magical.
  </p>

  <h2>Ready to Try?</h2>
  
  <p>
